  <brief_title>Effects of Bilateral GPI DBS on Freezing of Gait in PD</brief_title>
  <acronym>PD GPI DBS</acronym>
  <official_title>Effects of Bilateral Pallidal Deep Brain Stimulation on Freezing of Gait in Parkinson's Diseases</official_title>
